pcaspy
=======

pcaspy_ is a Portable Channel Access Server Python Binding. 
And it provides an easy API to create PCAS application in Python.

Prerequisites
--------------

  * EPICS base 3.14.8+ and environment variables EPICS_BASE and EPICS_HOST_ARCH are defined according to your actual EPICS base installation.
  * Python 2.4+
  * SWIG 1.3.29+

Build
---------------------
  * make

To build the current development, clone the project, 
  $ hg clone http://code.google.com/p/pcaspy/ pcaspy
